Yuno gets defeated by Nero, his Captain is taken away from him, and the rest of his fellowship is weakened and dead.
Asta trains with Nacht to control Liebe the demon within him, they have a long grueling bettle but Asta gets the edge and wins.
After training Asta learns the truth that Liebe is actually Atsa's stepbrother and her mother had an evil curse that killed any living organism around her except Liebe.
The king of the demons kills Asta's mom in hope's that he would be free from the demon world. 